For me personally, the number one metric is based on my happiness. And happiness here does not necessarily always mean pleasure or joy as I am doing it... I would imagine my future self reflecting on the decision that I am about to make, and see if I would be proud of feel a sense of contentment that I made the decision to do whatever I am about to do.

P.S. If you want to see the full interview, then go to @startcanadapodcast 👈 for the link.

node.text:
Do you you agree?👀 Your social media's feed says more about you then what's currently happening in the world. Part of the reason why you keep seeing negative news on your feed is because you keep interacting with those type of content. And the algorithm takes note of your behavior to keep feeding you content that you are likely to interact with...

Anyway, this is a snippet of an hour long interview I did with @startcanadapodcast 2 weeks ago where we talked about social media marketing for entrepreneurs.

Go check out their page @startcanadapodcast 👈to see the full episode if you want some free tips on growing your business utilizing social media as a tool. 📲

node.title: @iamdaviddang - Social media is just exposing us🙈

You are missing out by not sharing your knowledge to others. ⠀
⠀
Because most people are totally unaware of the value of their own knowledge and skills, and are unsure how to share what they know to others. ⠀
⠀
I’m willing to bet you didn’t know that the “self education” industry is exploding right now and projected by Forbes to TRIPLE in the next 5 years (most people don’t)...⠀
⠀
👉📲 🔗🔗Go to the link in my bio now @iamdaviddang if you'd like to take advantage of this!🔗🔗📲👈⠀
⠀
AND I’d bet even more that you don’t think it applies to you. ⠀
⠀
Here’s why you’re wrong:⠀
⠀
Whether you realize it or not, you have expertise, skills, hobbies, heck knowledge that people in the world want and need. You might not know what that is, but I’m telling you, YOU DO. ⠀
That’s where the “self education” industry comes in. People are willing to compensate experts for their knowledge, (I’ll repeat: experts like YOU)...⠀
⠀
So imagine this - what if you could harness that specialized knowledge you have and share it with the world…
⠀
And what if by doing that, you made an impact on peoples’ lives AND achieved the personal success you crave from it? ⠀
⠀
You may not realize it… but I’m impacting lives and making income myself as part of the “self education”industry. Crazy that this was so hidden before, right?!?⠀
⠀
Guess what!⠀
⠀
Dean Graziosi and Tony Robbins is doing a FREE 5 day Own Your Future Challenge to take back control of your career and future as the world is opening up again. You can use it to figure out what knowledge you have, learn how you could share it and get paid for it… so basically what I’m saying is...⠀
⠀
Welcome to your new life of sharing ;-)⠀
⠀
The free challenge begins on May 11th. Don’t miss this! Those average, “meh” filled days will be over if you decide right now to end them!⠀
⠀
👉📲 🔗🔗 CLICK THE LINK IN MY BIO @IAMDAVIDDANG TO REGISTER🔗🔗📲👈⠀
⠀
Or you can type in www.ownit63.com in your web browser to claim your spot before it's too late!👨‍💻

node.text:
People are afraid to take action and create a better future for themselves because they're too worried about what others will think of them.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Instead of learning how to REALLY make a difference in their lives, they work hard - as everybody does.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
The thing is... If hard work alone had helped to create success and wealth, everyone hardworking the 9-5 would have been a millionaire by now.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
There's a specific reason why out of 330 million people in the US, there are only 788 billionaires...⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
The key to success isn't working hard.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
The key to success is to be able to work smart.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Now you're probably asking: How can I learn to work smart?⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
That's why today, I highly recommend you to follow some of the best mentors on Instagram.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
The key to learning how to work smart and create your best future is by learning from the people who have already done it & teach you how you can do it too.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
Their daily Instagram posts will help you a lot.⁣⁣⁣⁣⁣
